para_trans: Lid of fun and white bandage of fun.
New as a "special case" at Gondia
Regarding sanction of Primary Health Centre.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / P.No.196 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. Station / Room-7A / T-5 / Precinct / Installation /
New Primary Health Centre sanctioned at Mauje Dhakani and Mauze Pandrabodi T.G. Gondia
A proposal to do so was under the consideration of the government.

The sanction of new Primary Health Centres at Maujey Dhakani and Maujey Pandharabodi T.G. Gondia is being approved under this Government Decision as a "special matter." For the above mentioned Primary Health Centre
Separate action will be taken by the Zilla Parishad to acquire the land in the prescribed manner and create the post after completion of the construction.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
